        Selling a Property With a Secondary Dwelling in Brisbane
      </h1>
      <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(240,236,228,0.6);line-height:1.8;max-width:54ch;">
        Granny flats, dual occupancy, and secondary dwellings add real complexity to a Brisbane sale. Here's what you need to sort out before you list.
      </p>
